column5: Finally got to my 1000th post. Never dreamed it when I joined up in 2004. It has been a great ride and I really enjoy all the contacts with all the lovers of Walleye Fishing. Walleye Central is a gift to us all and the avaliable information from fellow fisherman does make us all better fisherman and unites us in a great sport. Mike Kansas
Congrats Mike on your first 1,000 posts at WC......and here's to your next 1,000 posts ! Rich B
Mike Kansas, I sent you a PM
Henceforth you will be known as the Kansas Krank
Not even close to what my wife calls me. If this wasn't a family site I could repeat some of her favorite names for me. Mike Kansas
as they say..."as long as she doesnt call me late for dinner"
